48
00:04:18,804 --> 00:04:20,704
He asked me to come at 3:00.

49
00:04:20,704 --> 00:04:23,504
But, when I got here at the appointed time...

50
00:04:23,504 --> 00:04:26,704
The warning had already been executed.

51
00:04:26,704 --> 00:04:29,004
This seems to be the warning note.

52
00:04:29,004 --> 00:04:31,104
It was on the table.

53
