that's what I thought too.

57
00:04:43,304 --> 00:04:45,904
I'd like to see them try it!

58
00:04:49,704 --> 00:04:52,104
I didn't want his victim

59
00:04:52,104 --> 00:04:55,404
to become a killer.

60
00:04:55,404 --> 00:04:57,504
So before that,

61
00:04:57,504 --> 00:05:00,004
while the president was napping...

62
00:05:00,004 --> 00:05:01,704
Die!

