More pressing right now is the murder that was committed.

66
00:05:17,304 --> 00:05:20,304
Do you have any idea who the perpetrator might be?

67
00:05:20,304 --> 00:05:23,004
There were too many victims who had a grudge against him.

68
00:05:23,004 --> 00:05:26,804
But, is one of them really the murderer?

69
00:05:26,804 --> 00:05:28,304
Just what do you mean by that?

70
00:05:28,304 --> 00:05:29,304
Because...

71
00:05:29,304 --> 00:05:31,204
Inspector Megure.

72
00:05:31,204 --> 00:05:33,604
Did you come up with anything, medical examiner?

73
00:05:33,604 --> 00:05:34,604
Yes.

74
00:05:34,604 --> 00:05:37,004
The perpetrator, after knocking the victim unconscious,

75
00:05:37,004 --> 00:05:39,704
with a blunt object on the back of his head,

76
00:05:39,704 --> 00:05:43,404
seems to have choked him using a rope or something.

77
00:05:43,404 --> 00:05:47,304
We believe he died approximately two hours before the body was found.

78
00:05:47,304 --> 00:05:49,404
That would be around 1 pm.

79
00:05:49,404 --> 00:05:51,104
Inspector.

80
00:05:51,104 --> 00:05:54,404
He's the manager of this condominium.

81
00:05:54,404 --> 00:05:57,504
He's says he saw a suspicious woman just around that time.

82
00:05:57,504 --> 00:05:58,804
What?

83
00:05:58,804 --> 00:06:00,704
"Kinsaku Tomii (58)" -After eating lunch,

84
00:06:00,704 --> 00:06:04,404
I came up to this floor to do my rounds.

85
00:06:04,404 --> 00:06:06,904
Just then, from the direction of this room,

86
00:06:06,904 --> 00:06:10,604
I saw a blonde that I never saw before come walking towards me.

87
00:06:12,204 --> 00:06:15,204
I think it was just around 1 pm.

88
00:06:15,204 --> 00:06:16,204
Inspector.

89
00:06:18,204 --> 00:06:20,904
Does this woman look familiar?

90
00:06:22,704 --> 00:06:25,704
She's wearing sunglasses so it's hard to tell.

91
00:06:25,704 --> 00:06:29,704
But that doesn't necessarily have to be a woman, right?

92
00:06:29,704 --> 00:06:32,804
The person could've tried to look like one too.

93
00:06:32,804 --> 00:06:36,204
She's only seen leaving,

94
00:06:36,204 --> 00:06:38,204
so she could've secretly come in from the back door,

95
00:06:38,204 --> 00:06:40,704
and since she was witnessed,

96
00:06:40,704 --> 00:06:42,304
maybe she decided to leave from the front door on her way out.

97
00:06:42,304 --> 00:06:46,904
Didn't the president lock the door of his room?

98
00:06:48,104 --> 00:06:51,904
Come to think of it, the president had a habit of chain locking the door.

99
00:06:51,904 --> 00:06:54,904
Besides if he was concerned enough about the note

100
00:06:54,904 --> 00:06:57,104
to call on Pops, a detective,

101
00:06:57,104 --> 00:07:00,404
he wouldn't let anyone suspicious into the room, would he?

102
00:07:00,404 --> 00:07:04,804
Yeah, we haven't ruled out the fact that it could've been someone he knew.

103
00:07:04,804 --> 00:07:06,004
I got it!

104
00:07:06,004 --> 00:07:09,504
His family has finished identifying his body.

105
00:07:09,504 --> 00:07:12,104
His wife and younger brother are here, right?

106
00:07:12,104 --> 00:07:13,104
Let's go see them.

107
00:07:15,604 --> 00:07:20,104
"Mika Takarada (36)" -How should I go on living on my own from now on?

108
00:07:20,104 --> 00:07:21,204
"Koji Takarada (42)" -Darn it.

109
00:07:21,204 --> 00:07:25,004
Who'd do something like this to my precious older brother?

110
00:07:25,004 --> 00:07:26,104
Mrs. Takarada.

111
00:07:26,104 --> 00:07:30,504
Where were you at around 1 pm today?

112
00:07:30,504 --> 00:07:34,004
Are you suspecting me?

113
00:07:34,004 --> 00:07:37,804
No. This is just the routine.

114
00:07:37,804 --> 00:07:40,604
Of course they'll suspect you. Most naturally.

115
00:07:40,604 --> 00:07:43,804
Because you'll have assets and insurance money come avalanching in.

116
00:07:43,804 --> 00:07:47,504
Talk for yourself, you hated Takarada too!

117
00:07:47,504 --> 00:07:50,404
Where were you at around 1 pm?

118
00:07:50,404 --> 00:07:54,404
I was at home organizing the storeroom because Takarada asked me to.

119
00:07:54,404 --> 00:07:57,704
I see. What about you, Koji?

120
00:07:57,704 --> 00:08:01,504
I was out walking around Shinjuku.

121
00:08:01,504 --> 00:08:05,504
Do you have people who can verify for you?

122
00:08:08,404 --> 00:08:12,304
So I guess the answer's no.

123
00:08:12,304 --> 00:08:13,804
Excuse me.

124
00:08:13,804 --> 00:08:16,204
Mrs. Takarada's telling the truth!

125
00:08:16,204 --> 00:08:17,404
What?

126
00:08:17,404 --> 00:08:20,604
At a little after 2 pm when I left the house,

127
00:08:20,604 --> 00:08:22,504
I was in the study.

128
00:08:22,504 --> 00:08:24,404
But at around 1 pm,

129
00:08:24,404 --> 00:08:27,304
Mrs. Takarada was definitely in the storeroom.

130
00:08:27,304 --> 00:08:28,804
Shinkai.

131
00:08:28,804 --> 00:08:31,504
You're a lifesaver, thank you.

132
00:08:31,504 --> 00:08:32,604
No problem.

133
00:08:34,204 --> 00:08:35,504
Then...

134
00:08:35,504 --> 00:08:36,904
the only one left is.

135
00:08:36,904 --> 00:08:39,104
Hey.

136
00:08:39,104 --> 00:08:42,304
It's odd that you're narrowing it down to the family in the first place!

137
00:08:42,304 --> 00:08:43,304
Excuse me.

138
00:08:43,304 --> 00:08:46,704
Could I please ask you to continue this at the house?

139
00:08:50,304 --> 00:08:51,904
All right.

140
00:08:51,904 --> 00:08:54,104
Let's move places.

141
00:08:54,104 --> 00:08:56,404
-Me too. -Yeah.

142
00:08:56,404 --> 00:08:57,504
Officer Takagi.

143
00:08:57,504 --> 00:09:00,604
I want you to investigate the other case.

144
00:09:00,604 --> 00:09:02,204
Yes, sir.

145
00:09:05,304 --> 00:09:09,104
If only he had noticed that the president was dead...

146
00:09:09,104 --> 00:09:13,004
He wouldn't have had to commit the crime.

147
00:09:14,204 --> 00:09:16,304
"The Metropolitan Police Department"

148
00:09:16,304 --> 00:09:18,104
Making amends?

