00:09:18,104 --> 00:09:19,304
Yes.

150
00:09:19,304 --> 00:09:23,504
I was naturally aware of President Takarada's unscrupulous practices.

151
00:09:23,504 --> 00:09:25,804
But I convinced myself

152
00:09:25,804 --> 00:09:28,904
that his victims were fools for allowing themselves to be preyed upon.

153
00:09:28,904 --> 00:09:30,804
But the other day,

154
00:09:30,804 --> 00:09:34,004
one of them committed suicide

155
00:09:34,004 --> 00:09:35,604
along with his entire family.

156
00:09:36,704 --> 00:09:41,104
Their child, who died wasn't even a year old yet.

157
00:09:41,104 --> 00:09:42,604
And at that time for the first time,

158
00:09:42,604 --> 00:09:47,004
I blamed myself for playing a part in the president's evil deeds.

159
00:09:47,004 --> 00:09:50,404
Then this morning, I got that warning note of murder.

160
00:09:51,504 --> 00:09:53,404
I figured that the one who sent the note

161
00:09:53,404 --> 00:09:55,404
was in the same boat as the person

162
00:09:55,404 --> 00:09:59,304
