168
00:10:14,804 --> 00:10:17,104
So if I kill the president...

169
00:10:17,104 --> 00:10:20,004
since I played a part in helping the president,

170
00:10:20,004 --> 00:10:22,504
it would be a way to make amends.

171
00:10:22,504 --> 00:10:25,004
But, I didn't make it in time.

172
00:10:25,004 --> 00:10:27,904
That person had already committed the murder.

