00:11:43,604 --> 00:11:47,104
It seems to be true that a lot of people hated him.

199
00:11:47,104 --> 00:11:50,904
Then, you must've received a lot of threatening notes too?

200
00:11:50,904 --> 00:11:54,004
Yes and besides...

201
00:11:54,004 --> 00:11:55,704
Besides?

202
00:11:55,704 --> 00:11:57,004
What?

203
00:11:57,004 --> 00:11:58,804
What's odd?

