00:11:58,804 --> 00:12:04,204
It seems that Mr. Takarada used to get a lot of threatening notes.

205
00:12:04,204 --> 00:12:06,304
The maid also mentioned that there was a time

206
00:12:06,304 --> 00:12:09,204
