00:12:19,504 --> 00:12:23,404
More than that, he laughs it off in front of everyone at that time.

211
00:12:23,404 --> 00:12:27,104
Then he called you, right Pops?

212
00:12:27,104 --> 00:12:30,304
I wonder if he had any special reason to do so?

213
00:12:30,304 --> 00:12:32,104
I see!

214
00:12:32,104 --> 00:12:36,704
Mr. Takarada knew who was trying to kill him.

215
00:12:36,704 --> 00:12:38,304
That's why he deliberately laughed it off,

216
00:12:38,304 --> 00:12:40,704
so the perpetrator would get his guard down.

217
00:12:40,704 --> 00:12:44,104
Then he wanted me to investigate and nail the guy!

218
00:12:44,104 --> 00:12:46,304
I see. What?

219
00:12:46,304 --> 00:12:47,804
Which means...

220
00:12:49,304 --> 00:12:51,304
The perpetrator is a family member

221
00:12:51,304 --> 00:12:54,804
and one of the three who were there at that time!

222
00:12:54,804 --> 00:12:58,104
But, Pops, out of the three...

223
00:12:58,104 --> 00:13:01,804
Mr. Shinkai who stabbed Mr. Takarada

224
00:13:01,804 --> 00:13:04,604
without knowing that he was already strangled to death is ruled out.

225
00:13:04,604 --> 00:13:08,504
And if his wife Mika has an alibi...

226
00:13:08,504 --> 00:13:10,304
Then the only one left is...

227
00:13:10,304 --> 00:13:13,004
Hey. Hold it there.

228
00:13:15,104 --> 00:13:16,804
Yes, hello.

229
00:13:16,804 --> 00:13:20,404
Yes...

230
00:13:20,404 --> 00:13:21,604
Okay.

231
00:13:21,604 --> 00:13:25,504
They found fingerprints on the murder warning note.

232
00:13:25,504 --> 00:13:28,804
Mr. Koji Takarada, your fingerprints!

233
00:13:28,804 --> 00:13:31,904
No way...

234
00:13:31,904 --> 00:13:34,904
Kyoko, come here, will you?

235
00:13:34,904 --> 00:13:37,204
Yes, ma'am, did you call?

236
00:13:37,204 --> 00:13:41,104
Call my lawyer, Attorney Watari, and ask him to come here!

237
00:13:41,104 --> 00:13:43,604
Tell him I'd like to discuss inheritance processes with him.

238
00:13:43,604 --> 00:13:48,004
And contact Beika Life Insurance too because I'm the beneficiary.

239
00:13:48,004 --> 00:13:51,304
-Hurry! -Yes, ma'am.

240
00:13:51,304 --> 00:13:52,704
It's only natural, right?

241
00:13:52,704 --> 00:13:57,004
Because we've found that he's the perpetrator and the case is closed.

242
00:13:57,004 --> 00:14:01,304
No. We haven't concluded that yet.

243
00:14:01,304 --> 00:14:05,404
I've been waiting all this time for this moment to come!

244
00:14:05,404 --> 00:14:07,104
Now that it's over let me tell you.

245
00:14:07,104 --> 00:14:11,404
I only married Takarada for his money.

246
00:14:11,404 --> 00:14:16,504
Since he was notorious, I was anticipating that he would die early...

247
00:14:16,504 --> 00:14:18,704
Thank you so much, Koji.

248
00:14:21,904 --> 00:14:23,504
I feel dizzy.

249
00:14:23,504 --> 00:14:25,504
What's with her?

250
00:14:25,504 --> 00:14:27,504
At any rate, Koji,

251
00:14:27,504 --> 00:14:32,704
to make it look like the murder was committed by someone

252
00:14:32,704 --> 00:14:35,304
who hated Mr. Takarada you sent out the warning note,

253
00:14:35,304 --> 00:14:38,504
and killed him to take revenge

254
00:14:38,504 --> 00:14:40,704
for what he did to you two years ago.

255
00:14:40,704 --> 00:14:42,204
I didn't kill him.

256
00:14:42,204 --> 00:14:44,704
I didn't write any note threatening to kill him either.

257
00:14:44,704 --> 00:14:47,204
But, your fingerprints are on it!

258
00:14:48,404 --> 00:14:50,204
How strange.

259
00:14:50,204 --> 00:14:53,604
Why's he so composed?

260
00:14:53,604 --> 00:14:54,904
I see.

261
00:14:54,904 --> 00:14:56,004
Okay.

262
00:14:56,004 --> 00:14:59,304
Let me know if anything comes up.

